label: A2B_oC24_63_acg_f-001
title: URe$_{2}$ Structure
comments:
Above 180$^{\circ}$C URe$_{2}$ transforms from this structure to the \href{current_web_home_dir/AB2_hP12_194_f_ah-001}{$C14$ Hexagonal Laves structure}.  We use the data from (Hatt, 1961) taken at 20$^{\circ}$C. 
 Although the abstract of (Hatt, 1961) gives the space group as $Cmca$, the text of the paper correctly identifies it as $Cmcm$.
